<i>Oh, look, Ben. You should know by now
that we are a package deal.</i>

01:40.634 --> 01:42.401
<i>You buy one;
you get the other two for free.</i>

01:42.436 --> 01:43.735
Okay, when is this guy getting here?

01:43.771 --> 01:45.637
As long as you take it
within 72 hours we're good.

01:45.673 --> 01:49.341
Which means we still have
70 hours and 55 minutes.

01:50.494 --> 01:51.543
Okay, that must be him.

01:51.579 --> 01:53.479
<i>Oh, Jane. Turn your phone
to face the computer</i>

01:53.514 --> 01:54.680
<i>so that when I say, "I told you so,"</i>

01:54.715 --> 01:55.837
<i>I can see Kat's face.</i>

01:55.917 --> 01:57.749
