have a word with you.

03:44.458 --> 03:45.691
- Sure.
- Great.

03:45.726 --> 03:47.693
Great.

03:49.697 --> 03:52.297
<i>Kat, have you ever heard of Whole Spa?</i>

03:52.333 --> 03:54.700
They make the cleansers with
the rainbow labels, right?

03:54.735 --> 03:56.435
Yes, that's them.

03:56.470 --> 03:58.470
